@DATABASE "Bubble Dizzy"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - B - Bubble Dizzy"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - B
                   ====================================

                               Bubble Dizzy
                               ============


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(43232,0)"}         43232,0
@{"Infinite Energy" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(43198,0) zxampoke(45591,195)"}         43198,0:45591,195
@{"Skip Intro     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(60183,195)"}         60183,195


                         You might think "Why skip the intro? It's
                         cool!".. Well, OK.. It might be quite good
                         the first couple of times.. Then try it
                         after a few more goes, and it gets REALLY
                         annoying. So here's the solution.



                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
